pageProduct.name: QV Intensive Cream 500G
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Highly concentrated moisturising cream that helps prevent and relieve very dry skin.

Warnings

Avoid eyes.  For external use only. If irritation occurs, wash affected area and discontinue use.

Common Uses

QV Intensive Cream is a highly concentrated moisturising cream that helps prevent and relieve very dry skin. Suitable for use with eczema, dermatitis and psoriasis. Also suitable for infants and the elderly.

Ingredients

Aqua (Water), Petrolatum, Paraffinum Liquidum, Glycerin, Cyclopentasiloxane, Cyclohexasiloxane, Cetearyl Alcohol, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Dimethicone, 1,2-Hexanediol, Caprylyl Glycol

Directions

Apply liberally to the face and body and massage in gently. Use after bathing and showering.  Use in conjunction with QV Intensive Moisturising Cleanser.
